Author: Ottermandias
Name: Accountant
Description: 집사, 비공정, 잠수함, 일일/주간 복권 등 타이머를 표시해주는 플러그인입니다.

Author: Tischel
Name: ActionTimeline
Description: 한 행동들을 보여주는 설정 가능한 타임라인

Author: Helios
Name: Adaptive Hud
Punchline: 전체화면모드와 창모드로 전환할 때 /hudlayout 을 자동으로 적용해보세요.
Description:
울트라와이드 모니터 사용자에게 유용하며, 전체화면/창모드 전환 시에 자동으로 HUD 레이아웃을 변경해줍니다.

명령어 : /pah

Author: Caraxi
Name: Adventurer in Need
Punchline: 무작위 임무에 부족한 역할군이 생기면 알림을 받습니다.
Description:
무작위 임무에 부족한 역할군이 생기면 알림을 받습니다.

명령어 : /pbonus

Author: Critical_Impact
Name: Allagan Tools
Punchline: Get organized in FFXIV, easily locate/show where to sort items, plan your crafting, and search for mobs, duties, airships, and submarines!
Description:
Allagan Tool's primary purpose is to keep track of items across your characters/retainers/free company. With it's filter system you'll never lose track of items or not know where they should be sorted.

While this is it's primary purpose, it has quite an exhaustive list of other features including:
	- Craft planning
	- Market board integration
	- Item highlighting in inventories when searching/sorting and picking ingredients for crafts
	- Item window that includes vendor and source information among other things
	- Duty/mob/airship/submarine windows that are fully searchable
	- A filtering system that lets you setup complex searches for specific items 
	- Tooltip integration that'll let you see where the items are on hover

Author: Gotest
Name: Audible Character Status
Punchline: You like annoying low HP sounds? This is great for you!
Description:
Plays a sound for certain statuses of the player. Such as low HP or MP.
You will need to provide your own sound files.

Author: Infi
Name: Better Playtime
Punchline: 초단위로 오늘의 접속시간을 보고 싶지 않으신가요?
Description:
Provides expanded functionality to seamlessly track total playtime.
 Use /btime once on each character to add them.

 - Supports multiple characters,
 - Customisable output formats such as hours or minutes
 - Automatic playtime tracking after character got registered
 - Simple window to see current session playtime
 - Server Info Bar integration

Author: d87
Name: BigPlayerDebuffs
Description: 대상에게 건 디버프를 크게 보여줍니다.

Author: ascclemens
Name: Chat 2
Punchline: Electric Boogaloo - ♪ 완전히 새로운 채팅창, 새로운 창에 표시 ♪
Description:
Chat 2는 새로운 창에 인게임 채팅창을 구현합니다.
지원하는 기능:

- 무제한 탭
- 특정 채팅 채널로 보내주는 탭
- 보다 유연한 필터링
- RGB 컬러링
- 자유로운 폰트 크기
- 사이드바 방식의 탭
- 읽지 않은 메시지 표시
- 스크린샷 모드 (obfuscate names)

Author: Haplo064, Khayle
Name: Chat Bubbles
Description: Using native chat bubble display, see who is talking about what in a more natural fashion.

Author: Chivalrik
Name: Compass
Description:
Check-out the repository for steps on how to report missing/wrong filter
and hiding options. Have a look at the FAQ tab in the config window
after install for common caveats.

Author: MidoriKami
Name: Daily Duty
Description:
일일/주간 할일을 자동으로 표시해줍니다.

/dd help → 모든 명령어 표시

Author: perchbird
Name: Damage Info
Punchline: 보다 많은(또는 적은) 인게임 데미지 정보
Description: 다양하게 설정 가능한 인게임 데미지 표시

Author: Kouzukii
Name: Death Recap
Punchline: Quickly figure out what killed you or your party members!
Description:
Quickly figure out what killed you or your party members!

Shows:
- Healing
- Damage taken
- Debuffs
- Buffs
- Barriers
- Addle, Feint, Reprisal on damage source

Author: goat, modded by Franz
Name: Discord Chat Bridge
Description: 이 플러그인은 인게임 채팅을 디스코드로 받을 수 있게 해줍니다.

Author: goat
Name: Discord Rich Presence
Punchline: 디스코드 상태로 당신의 게임 정보를 표시하세요.
Description: 이 플러그인은 당신의 위치, 직업, 레벨, 이름, 그리고 서버를 디스코드 상태에 표시해줍니다.

Author: PunishedPineapple
Name: Distance
Description: 대상과의 거리(또는 설정에 따라서 테두리와의 거리)를 얄름(y)로 보여주며, 지원되는 보스들과의 거리도 보여줍니다.

Author: Speedas
Name: Emote log
Description: 몰래 쓴 /애정을 놓치지 않도록, 감정표현을 받은 기록 창을 추가합니다.

Author: Xorus
Name: EngageTimer
Description:
초읽기 플러그인

기능들 :
- 커다란 초읽기
- 커스텀 가능한 숫자 (기본, 노랑, WoW 스타일 또는 커스텀 파일)
- 서버 정보 바, 또 다른 창에 전투 시간 표시
- 초읽기와 현재 전투 시간에 대한 OBS 브라우저 소스 지원

녹화할 때 OBS가 필요할지도 모르잖아요?

Author: NightmareXIV
Name: EnemyListHP (former EnmityHp)
Punchline: Displays enemies hp in enemy list.
Description: Displays enemies hp in enemy list. Just does that, nothing else.

Author: daemitus
Name: ezMiniCactpot
Punchline: Shows the next best move in Mini Cactpot.
Description: This plugin highlights tiles and lines in MiniCactpot that represent the best potential action you can take.

Author: Caraxi
Name: FPS Plugin
Description: Display game FPS. It really is that simple.

Author: Ottermandias
Name: GatherBuddy
Description:
Adds commands to simplify gathering by finding nodes and fish and their locations
via item name and a UI to keep track of special uptime and weather conditions.

Author: ascclemens
Name: Glamaholic
Description: 원하는 만큼의 투영 세트를 저장하세요. 20개 이상 저장할 수 있습니다. export와 import 지원.

Author: Ottermandias
Name: Glamourer
Punchline: Change and save appearance of players.
Description: Adds functionality to change and store appearance of players, customization and equip. Requires Penumbra to be installed and activated to work. Can also add preview options to the Changed Items tab for Penumbra.

Author: ascclemens
Name: Globetrotter
Punchline: Automatically shows where treasure maps are located.
Description:
Automatically shows where treasure maps are located.

Icon: Map by Adrien Coquet from the Noun Project

Author: MgAl2O4
Name: Harp Hero
Description:
연주를 하고 싶지만 어떻게 하는지 모르는 바드들을 위한 '어시스트' 플러그인.
- 자동으로 연주해주는 것이 절대 아님
- MIDI 파일 필요
- adapts MIDI tracks to fit in game limitations for you
- you will be scored :O

Author: perchbird
Name: Housemate
Description:
Housemate offers multiple features that help you gain inspiration from other homes in XIV.
If you're looking for a specific home or outdoor item, you can check the exterior list
when running around a ward. If you're interested in seeing what items make up a
structure in a home - turn on the item overlay to see what they are!

Note: This plugin is purely informational, and does not assist you in placing
or "glitching" housing items.

Author: Gotest
Name: Kingdom Hearts UI Bars
Punchline: HP bar, MP bar, EXP bar, oh my!
Description:
A plugin that makes Kingdom Hearts UI stuff, such as a health bar for the player.
If you have any questions, issues or suggestions, please post an issue in the github or ping me in the Discord!

Author: Caraxi
Name: Macro Chain
Description:
매크로의 마지막 줄에 '/nextmacro' 를 넣어서 다음 매크로가 이어서 실행되게 합니다.
1번 매크로의 마지막 줄에 '/nextmacro' 를 입력해두면, 자동으로 2번 매크로가 실행됩니다.
1번 매크로의 마지막 줄에 '/nextmacro down' 를 입력해두면 자동으로 11번 매크로가 실행됩니다.
또한, 채팅창에 '/runmacro' 를 입력하면 그 매크로를 실행해주지만, 매크로 내에서 사용할 수는 없습니다.

Author: Bluefissure
Name: MapLinker
Description: 채팅에 깃발을 기록해두고, 나중에도 찾아볼 수 있습니다.

Author: Meli & perchbird
Name: Orchestrion Plugin
Punchline: Adds a simple front-end for browsing and changing the in-game BGM.
Description:
Orchestrion Plugin allows you to change the currently playing in-game BGM. It includes
a curated list of the most accurate in-game song titles, so you know exactly what's playing,
if you want to know later! Add favorite songs to separate them from the rest.
Note: This plugin does not currently allow you to play actual orchestrion songs.

Author: MgAl2O4
Name: Pat Me
Description: Did you ever wonder how many times your Lala gets a pat? Well, now you can count it!

Author: ascclemens
Name: Peeping Tom
Punchline: Shows who is currently or was previously targeting you.
Description: Shows who is currently or was previously targeting you.

Author: Haplo064
Name: Pixel Perfect
Punchline: Reveals your hitbox, with customisable features.
Description: Showing exactly where to stand since 2020.

Author: UnknownX
Name: QoL Bar
Description:
A plugin designed to provide a simple, customizable and always available interface for chat commands
or other plugins to alleviate the need for using macros and hotbar space to achieve similar results.

The plugin should initially appear as a small box on the bottom center of the game window.

Author: PunishedPineapple
Name: Ready Check Helper
Punchline: Extends the game's built-in ready check.
Description: Displays the names of the players that were not ready in chat following the completion of a ready check, and optionally adds ready check status icons over the party and alliance lists.

Author: ascclemens
Name: Remote Party Finder Uploader
Punchline: Crowdsourced PF website (upload PF listings to xivpf.xyz)
Description:
Uploads the PF listings you retrieve to the crowdsourced Remote
Party Finder website (https://xivpf.xyz/).

Author: Chalkos
Name: RepairMe
Punchline: Never forget to repair & extract materia again!
Description: Helps you notice when your gear needs to be repaired or has materia to be extracted.

Author: Ottermandias
Name: RezPls
Punchline: Highlighting of Raises and detrimental status effects.
Description:
Easy overview about who is currently resurrecting who,
who is already resurrected,
and who has removable detrimental status effects in the world 
as well as in the group or alliance interface.

Author: Caraxi
Name: Simple Tweaks Plugin
Punchline: This was supposed to be simple...
Description:
A collection of Quality of Life tweaks. Aiming to improve the experience without changing anything drastically.
All changes are toggleable, with everything disabled by default. Visit the Repo for a full list of tweaks. (Globe icon below)

Author: NightmareXIV
Name: Splatoon
Description: Adds custom waymark system into the game, allowing drawing infinite amount of waymarks in world and highlighting objects, players and enemies.

Author: Pohky
Name: Teleporter
Description:
Adds Chat Commands to Teleport to Aetherytes or Areas by Name.
e.g. /tp Quarrymill or /tpm South Shroud
Supports setting up an Alias for Aetherytes to be used with Teleporter Commands
e.g. /tp home instead of /tp Estate Hall (Free Company)

Author: MgAl2O4
Name: TriadBuddy
Description:
Triple triad solver, NPC matches only.
- highlights next move during mini game
- evaluates all deck presets before match
- deck optimizer for NPC
- adds more details to card collection window

Author: ascclemens
Name: Tourist
Description:
Tourist adds a window to assist with the sightseeing log.

- Show when sightseeing log vistas are available
- Add markers for ARR vistas
- Open vista locations on your map
- Hide already completed or unavailable vistas
- Show the command needed for each vista

Icon: sightseeing by muhammad from the Noun Project

Author: goat
Name: Ultrawide Cutscenes
Punchline: Remove letterboxing from cutscenes on ultrawide monitors.
Description:
This plugin removes the "letterboxing" bars when watching cutscenes on ultrawide monitors.
Beware! You may see things that you are not supposed to be seeing, such as upcoming NPCs popping in or T-posing.

Thanks to aers for finding this.

Author: ocealot
Name: VFXEditor
Description: VFX, animation, and sound editing plugin. Icon by PAPACHIN

Author: PunishedPineapple, squidmade
Name: Waymark Preset Plugin
Description: Allows you to save, edit, place, import, export, and preview an unlimited number of waymark presets.

Author: Attick
Name: XIV Combo
Description: This plugin condenses combos and mutually exclusive abilities onto a single button. /pcombo to open menu

Author: LeonBlade
Name: Heels Plugin
Description: Offsets your character off the ground for when wearing heels.

Author: Jawslouis
Name: MakePlace Plugin
Description: Automatically save & load interior and exterior house layouts. Import/export layouts from the MakePlace program.
Punchline: Automatically save & load furniture layouts in your house.

Author: LeonBlade
Name: Burning Down the House
Description: 하우징 아이템들을 위치 제약에 상관없이 설치해보세요.

Author: shdwp, Avaflow, squidmade
Name: Party Icons
Punchline: Replace names with job icons, raid role positions and more!
Description:
Adjusts player nameplates base on current content. For example you can display raid positions (that are assigned automatically by listening to the chat), job icons, or names with job icons.

Reverse-engineering effort achieved by authors of JobIcons: haplo, daemitus, Loskh, wozaiha, without them this plugin would not be possible!

Author: Chirp
Name: Ktisis
Punchline: A robust posing tool for creating screenshots in GPose.
Description: A robust posing tool for creating screenshots in GPose.

Author: ocealot
Name: JobBars
Description: Additional job gauges, party buff timers, mitigation trackers, and more. Icon by PAPACHIN

Author: Adam
Name: Penumbra
Description: Runtime mod loader and manager.
